sunyo je kol ( bengali : শূন্য যে কোল , english : the empty lap ) is a 2016 bengali film with story , screenplay , dialogues and direction by bhaswati roy . the film revolves on the issue of surrogate motherhood . dr rajesh das , bhaswati ’s husband , and four of his doctor friends from calcutta medical college act in her debut film . the film had a limited release on january 29 , 2016 .